<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
Only accessible to the lost soul subrace. <p>
Unique monsters are never generated in The Halls of Mandos (as far as I can tell), though they can be summoned as per usual; thus, genocide is more useful here than elsewhere.  Dungeon towns can be generated, but don't count on it; none of the several Lost Souls I have escaped with ever saw one, although a few who died on the way did. 
</p>
<p>
See the subrace spoiler <a href="./Spoilers_2fSubraces_2fLost_20Soul">Spoilers/Subraces/Lost Soul</a> for tons of tips for surviving twenty extra turns or so in this near-hopeless environnement!!! 
</p>
